snippet.title: 2 Minutes of Netflix Infinite Runner Gameplay
snippet.description:
Netflix has created a browser based "game" based on a few of its most popular TV series including Stranger Things, Narcos, Orange Is the New Black, and Marco Polo.

Check out the game here: https://flixarcade.netflix.io/
